                <mxCell id="p4_insight" value="&lt;b&gt;The Key Insight:&lt;/b&gt; Same Python test scripts run against ALL four quadrants. Only the &lt;b&gt;exporter configuration&lt;/b&gt; changes. One framework eliminates toolchain sprawl." style="text;html=1;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Red Hat Text;fontColor=#EE0000;align=center;" parent="1" vertex="1">
