                <mxCell id="p5_ph3_v2" value="• Vehicles that improve after sale&lt;br&gt;• Predictive maintenance, targeted recalls&lt;br&gt;• Closed-loop: fleet data → retraining → OTA&lt;br&gt;• Full competitive parity with Tesla-like cadence" style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;fontFamily=Red Hat Text;fontColor=#151515;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
